            "mimeType": "application/json",
            "size": 2106,
            "text": "[{\"thread_number\":0,\"last_query_datetime\":\"2026-05-24T12:38:48.639246\",\"mode\":\"asi\",\"context_uuid\":\"594e708c-fc79-4f6d-a155-f2cdbdd0ab44\",\"uuid\":\"c230e361-f09a-492d-b5bd-be00d822fbf1\",\"frontend_uuid\":\"da78ee54-defa-4e46-a7be-5dd49bf13bb9\",\"frontend_context_uuid\":\"6be2f572-dfb8-4d26-b9fa-6b01d822e0b2\",\"slug\":\"c230e361-f09a-492d-b5bd-be00d822fbf1\",\"title\":\"Using Network Printers as Jump Boxes\",\"query_str\":\"Are there any options of using printers on a network which is behind a private Ip to use as a jump box for that network using a VPs or self hosted tunnel.?\",\"first_answer\":\"{\\\"answer\\\":\\\"Yes. If you want no WireGuard package and no extra tunnel agent, use native OpenSSH reverse tunneling. Windows includes OpenSSH as a supported optional/built-in capability, and Microsoft documents SSH reverse tunnels as a pattern where the internal/on-prem host opens an outbound SSH connection so no inbound firewall port is needed on the private network ([Microsoft...\\\"}\",\"answer_preview\":\"Yes. If you want no WireGuard package and no extra tunnel agent, use native OpenSSH reverse tunneling. Windows includes OpenSSH as a supported optional/built-in capability, and Microsoft documents SSH reverse tunnels as a pattern where the internal/on-prem host opens an outbound SSH connection so no inbound firewall port is needed on the private network ([Microsoft...\",\"thread_access\":1,\"has_next_page\":true,\"status\":\"COMPLETED\",\"display_model\":\"PPLX_ASI\",\"expiry_time\":null,\"source\":\"ios\",\"source_metadata\":null,\"thread_status\":\"completed\",\"thread_status_summary\":null,\"thread_status_summary_enum\":null,\"locked_reason\":null,\"wake_at\":null,\"crons\":null,\"stream_created_at\":null,\"persona_id\":null,\"query_source\":null,\"dream_mode\":null,\"last_entry_uuid\":\"828e30db-6ea0-4fe6-a3ea-429c6eb063b8\",\"latest_elapsed_time\":45.632258,\"unread\":false,\"query_count\":1,\"search_focus\":\"writing\",\"sources\":[],\"featured_images\":[],\"read_write_token\":\"6a5b091c-e371-4d66-9dec-eeacc6e04e7e\",\"total_threads\":99,\"social_info\":{\"view_count\":0,\"fork_count\":0,\"like_count\":0,\"user_likes\":false},\"assets\":[],\"num_assets\":0,\"attachments\":[]}]"
