          "content": {
            "mimeType": "application/json",
            "size": 8595,
            "text": "{\"primers\":[{\"uuid\":\"for_you\",\"type\":\"QUERY\",\"action\":{\"type\":\"POPULATE_INPUT\",\"input_prefix\":\"\",\"homepage_tagline\":null,\"suggestions\":[{\"query\":\"Draft a campus event briefing deck with roles, timing, and fallback plans, ready to review with volunteers this week\",\"submission_query\":\"I'm coordinating university events — pull upcoming dates, notes, and open tasks from my calendar and Notion, then draft a briefing deck with run-of-show, staffing plan, media needs, and fallback actions. Make it ready to review with volunteers or faculty this week.\",\"query_source\":\"personalized_computer\",\"model_preference\":null,\"uuid\":null},{\"query\":\"Capture repo changes into Notion automatically, so each experiment keeps a usable setup log and next steps\",\"submission_query\":\"Next time I update or create a GitHub repo for an agent or trading tool, summarize the changes, setup steps, and open questions into Notion automatically. Keep a clean project log so each experiment has searchable notes and a next-step section.\",\"query_source\":\"personalized_computer\",\"model_preference\":null,\"uuid\":null},{\"query\":\"Build a live wallet exposure dashboard, so you can see concentration, transfers, and risk shifts in one place\",\"submission_query\":\"Build a live crypto exposure dashboard for the wallets and positions I'm watching. Pull balances, token concentration, recent transfers, and PnL proxies into one view, and flag when exposure shifts sharply or a single asset dominates the stack.\",\"query_source\":\"personalized_computer\",\"model_preference\":null,\"uuid\":null}],\"trigger_location_prompt\":false,\"trigger_file_tooltip\":false,\"trigger_deep_research\":false,\"trigger_labs\":false,\"trigger_study_mode\":false,\"trigger_source\":null},\"query\":\"For you\",\"prompt\":\"For you\",\"dismissable\":false,\"icon_url\":null,\"icon_reference\":\"sparkles\",\"educational_type\":\"primer\",\"personalized\":true,\"is_new\":false},{\"uuid\":\"output_vertical_make_spreadsheets\",\"type\":\"QUERY\",\"action\":{\"type\":\"POPULATE_INPUT\",\"input_prefix\":\"\",\"homepage_tagline\":null,\"suggestions\":[{\"query\":\"Build one live SEPS calendar for events, posts, and missing assets, so nothing slips before publish day\",\"submission_query\":\"Build a live spreadsheet that combines upcoming calendar events, content deadlines, and asset status for SEPS work. Group by week, highlight missing copy or media, and make it easy to see what needs approval first.\",\"query_source\":\"output_vertical\",\"model_preference\":null,\"uuid\":null},{\"query\":\"Compare today's lowest-cost AI model options in one workbook, with a routing matrix for coding and bulk jobs this week\",\"submission_query\":\"I'm testing too many model endpoints. Research the current free and cheapest options across Vertex, GitHub Models, Cloudflare, and Bedrock, normalize rate limits and context windows, and deliver a comparison workbook plus a recommended routing matrix for coding, research, and cheap bulk jobs.\",\"query_source\":\"output_vertical\",\"model_preference\":null,\"uuid\":null}],\"trigger_location_prompt\":false,\"trigger_file_tooltip\":false,\"trigger_deep_research\":false,\"trigger_labs\":false,\"trigger_study_mode\":false,\"trigger_source\":null},\"query\":\"Make spreadsheets\",\"prompt\":\"Make spreadsheets\",\"dismissable\":false,\"icon_url\":null,\"icon_reference\":\"table\",\"educational_type\":\"primer\",\"personalized\":true,\"is_new\":false},{\"uuid\":\"output_vertical_build_apps_and_tools\",\"type\":\"QUERY\",\"action\":{\"type\":\"POPULATE_INPUT\",\"input_prefix\":\"\",\"homepage_tagline\":null,\"suggestions\":[{\"query\":\"Build a shell-command test harness and fix checklist, so agent-run scripts stop failing on multiline jobs\",\"submission_query\":\"Every now and then complex shell commands break inside coding agents. Research the common failure modes, build a small test harness that reproduces them, and write a hardening checklist with safer command patterns I can reuse across projects.\",\"query_source\":\"output_vertical\",\"model_preference\":null,\"uuid\":null},{\"query\":\"Ship a cTrader paper-trading sandbox with order logs, so you can test execution flows before risking capital\",\"submission_query\":\"I'm researching cTrader and trading MCP options — assemble the best current repos and API docs, then build a paper-trading sandbox that can place, cancel, and log simulated orders from a simple local interface. Success is a reusable repo with config templates and a fill log I can review after sessions.\",\"query_source\":\"output_vertical\",\"model_preference\":null,\"uuid\":null},{\"query\":\"Turn the wallet analyzer into a reusable local tool with exported reports, ready for repeat checks on new addresses\",\"submission_query\":\"Take the Hyperliquid wallet analyzer I was looking at and turn it into a clean local tool I can rerun on any address. Package setup steps, config, report export, and a sample output so I have a repeatable workflow instead of a one-off install.\",\"query_source\":\"output_vertical\",\"model_preference\":null,\"uuid\":null}],\"trigger_location_prompt\":false,\"trigger_file_tooltip\":false,\"trigger_deep_research\":false,\"trigger_labs\":false,\"trigger_study_mode\":false,\"trigger_source\":null},\"query\":\"Build apps and tools\",\"prompt\":\"Build apps and tools\",\"dismissable\":false,\"icon_url\":null,\"icon_reference\":\"app-window\",\"educational_type\":\"primer\",\"personalized\":true,\"is_new\":false},{\"uuid\":\"output_vertical_build_website\",\"type\":\"QUERY\",\"action\":{\"type\":\"POPULATE_INPUT\",\"input_prefix\":\"\",\"homepage_tagline\":null,\"suggestions\":[{\"query\":\"Publish a private lab docs site for my agent setups, so working configs and fixes stop living in scattered notes\",\"submission_query\":\"I'm constantly reinstalling and tweaking agent tooling. Pull setup notes from my GitHub repos and Notion, organize them by tool, model, and platform, and publish a private docs site with install steps, known issues, and working configs.\",\"query_source\":\"output_vertical\",\"model_preference\":null,\"uuid\":null},{\"query\":\"Launch a searchable MCP server index with setup notes, so you can pick the right tool fast without repo-hopping\",\"submission_query\":\"Go through the best current GitHub repos for MCP servers relevant to browser control, trading, and coding workflows. Score install quality, maintenance, auth model, and UI fit, then publish a searchable site with tags, setup notes, and links to the repos worth trying first.\",\"query_source\":\"output_vertical\",\"model_preference\":null,\"uuid\":null}],\"trigger_location_prompt\":false,\"trigger_file_tooltip\":false,\"trigger_deep_research\":false,\"trigger_labs\":false,\"trigger_study_mode\":false,\"trigger_source\":null},\"query\":\"Build website\",\"prompt\":\"Build website\",\"dismissable\":false,\"icon_url\":null,\"icon_reference\":\"world-www\",\"educational_type\":\"primer\",\"personalized\":true,\"is_new\":false},{\"uuid\":\"output_vertical_schedule_automations\",\"type\":\"QUERY\",\"action\":{\"type\":\"POPULATE_INPUT\",\"input_prefix\":\"\",\"homepage_tagline\":null,\"suggestions\":[{\"query\":\"Capture repo changes into Notion automatically, so each experiment keeps a usable setup log and next steps\",\"submission_query\":\"Next time I update or create a GitHub repo for an agent or trading tool, summarize the changes, setup steps, and open questions into Notion automatically. Keep a clean project log so each experiment has searchable notes and a next-step section.\",\"query_source\":\"output_vertical\",\"model_preference\":null,\"uuid\":null},{\"query\":\"Get a Monday-ready event ops brief from my inbox and calendar, with deadlines and missing pieces called out\",\"submission_query\":\"Every Sunday evening, compile next week's university events and communications into a short ops brief from Gmail, Calendar, and Notion. Include deadlines, owners, unresolved asks, and a one-screen summary I can forward Monday morning.\",\"query_source\":\"output_vertical\",\"model_preference\":null,\"uuid\":null},{\"query\":\"Track model pricing and limit changes automatically, and get pinged only when a better route is worth switching to\",\"submission_query\":\"Next time model pricing, limits, or free-tier terms change for the providers I keep testing, refresh my tracker automatically and email me only when a route becomes materially cheaper or more capable. Keep a dated changelog and a short recommendation note for what to switch this week.\",\"query_source\":\"output_vertical\",\"model_preference\":null,\"uuid\":null}],\"trigger_location_prompt\":false,\"trigger_file_tooltip\":false,\"trigger_deep_research\":false,\"trigger_labs\":false,\"trigger_study_mode\":false,\"trigger_source\":null},\"query\":\"Schedule automations\",\"prompt\":\"Schedule automations\",\"dismissable\":false,\"icon_url\":null,\"icon_reference\":\"calendar-repeat\",\"educational_type\":\"primer\",\"personalized\":true,\"is_new\":false}]}"
          },
