          "content": {
            "mimeType": "application/json",
            "size": 8660,
            "text": "{\"cards\":[{\"id\":\"schedule-a-recurring-task\",\"icon\":\"calendar-repeat\",\"title\":\"Schedule a recurring task\",\"query\":\"Help me schedule a recurring task for something I care about. Ask me the goal, which apps to work with, the cadence, and how I want the output delivered (doc, spreadsheet, deck, dashboard), then set it up and produce the first run.\"},{\"id\":\"build-a-research-agent\",\"icon\":\"robot\",\"title\":\"Build a research agent\",\"query\":\"Help me set up a recurring research agent. Ask me my field, then show 3–5 example research questions with rationale and let me pick one or write my own. Once I commit, ask me the journals or sources, frequency, and delivery format (email, doc, slides, or live dashboard), then build a live research feed and schedule it.\"},{\"id\":\"build-an-app\",\"icon\":\"device-mobile\",\"title\":\"Build an app\",\"query\":\"Help me build an app. Ask me whether I have a concept in mind. If not, show 4–6 example app ideas across categories (productivity, internal tool, consumer utility, AI assistant, marketplace) and let me pick one or describe my own. Once I commit, ask me the platform (web, mobile, desktop, internal) and must-have features, then build a working web app and deploy it to a live URL I can share.\"},{\"id\":\"run-a-final-pass\",\"icon\":\"checks\",\"title\":\"Run a final pass\",\"query\":\"Help me run a final pass on a document before I hit send. Ask me what the document is, the audience, what to focus on (errors, inconsistencies, unverified claims, tone), and any house style to follow, then return a redlined Word doc with inline annotations and a one-page issues summary.\"},{\"id\":\"create-a-report\",\"icon\":\"report\",\"title\":\"Create a report\",\"query\":\"Help me create a report. Ask me what it is about, who it is for, what format I want, and whether I have source material or examples to model it after, then draft the report.\"},{\"id\":\"build-a-website\",\"icon\":\"browser\",\"title\":\"Build a website\",\"query\":\"Help me build a website. Ask me my purpose and audience, then show 4–5 example site archetypes (portfolio, landing, blog, storefront, docs) with rationale and let me pick one or describe my own. Once I commit, ask me the site name, style preferences, and content sections I need, then plan the design, build it, and deploy it.\"},{\"id\":\"debug-an-issue-in-prod\",\"icon\":\"bug\",\"title\":\"Debug an issue in prod\",\"query\":\"Help me debug a production bug. First, ask me to connect my code repo, monitoring tools, and error tracker so you can pull logs, traces, recent deploys, and changes automatically. Then ask me the error message and expected vs. actual behavior, reproduce the issue, identify the root cause, and open a pull request with the fix and tests.\"},{\"id\":\"debug-my-code\",\"icon\":\"bug\",\"title\":\"Debug my code\",\"query\":\"Help me debug my code. Ask me for the repo or files, the error I am seeing, and what should happen instead, then find the issue and fix it.\"},{\"id\":\"triage-my-email-inbox\",\"icon\":\"mail\",\"title\":\"Triage my email inbox\",\"query\":\"Help me create a recurring agent that triages my inbox and drafts replies for my review. First, ask me to connect my email so you can read and act on incoming threads. Then ask me the senders or topics that need priority, my tone preferences, and how often to run, and produce a daily triage digest with prioritized threads and draft replies.\"},{\"id\":\"visualize-my-data\",\"icon\":\"chart-pie\",\"title\":\"Visualize my data\",\"query\":\"Help me visualize my data. Ask me what question I want to answer, where the data lives, and what kind of chart or dashboard I want, then create a clear visualization.\"},{\"id\":\"create-a-spreadsheet\",\"icon\":\"file-spreadsheet\",\"title\":\"Create a spreadsheet\",\"query\":\"Help me build a useful spreadsheet. Ask me what I want to track, calculate, or analyze, what data I have, and whether I have examples to model it after, then create a downloadable spreadsheet with formulas.\"},{\"id\":\"report-daily-kpis\",\"icon\":\"chart-line\",\"title\":\"Report daily KPIs\",\"query\":\"Help me create a daily agent that reports key metrics for my business. First, ask me to connect my billing, product analytics, and data warehouse so you can pull metrics automatically. Then ask me which metrics matter, the cadence, and the delivery channel, and build a live KPI dashboard and schedule the daily report.\"},{\"id\":\"build-a-personal-assistant\",\"icon\":\"robot\",\"title\":\"Build a personal assistant\",\"query\":\"Help me build a personal assistant agent that does work for me on a recurring basis. First, recommend some ways a personal assistant powered by Computer can be helpful. Then, connect to my email, calendar, messaging, document store, and notes so the agent can read and act across them. Finally, ask me what I want help with, my time zone, and how I want updates delivered, and produce a one-page runbook of what the agent does and when.\"},{\"id\":\"in-depth-market-research\",\"icon\":\"world-search\",\"title\":\"Research a market\",\"query\":\"Help me run in-depth market research. Ask me the company or market, then show 2–3 example framework bundles (Porter's + TAM/SAM, JTBD + Wardley, SWOT + competitive) with rationale and let me pick one or define my own. Once I commit, ask me the focus area and output format, then produce a polished PDF report and a companion slide deck with sourced charts.\"},{\"id\":\"automate-a-workflow\",\"icon\":\"vector-spline\",\"title\":\"Automate a workflow\",\"query\":\"Help me automate a task. Ask me what goal I want to achieve, what steps I repeat today, which apps or websites are involved, and when the automation should run.\"},{\"id\":\"build-an-internal-tool\",\"icon\":\"tool\",\"title\":\"Build an internal tool\",\"query\":\"Help me build a small internal tool. Ask me the problem, who uses it, must-have features, my stack preferences, and where it should be hosted, then build and deploy a working version.\"},{\"id\":\"run-my-week\",\"icon\":\"calendar-week\",\"title\":\"Run my week\",\"query\":\"Help me create a recurring chief of staff agent that manages my week and sends daily updates. Connect to my calendar, email, and project tools. Analyze my meetings, threads, top initiatives, and recent documents automatically. Share a daily briefing of my top to dos and action items.\"},{\"id\":\"set-a-reminder\",\"icon\":\"bell\",\"title\":\"Set a reminder\",\"query\":\"Help me set a reminder. Ask me what I need to remember, when to remind me, what timezone to use, and whether it should repeat, then schedule it and produce a shareable plan or checklist for what to do when it fires.\"},{\"id\":\"ship-a-pr\",\"icon\":\"git-pull-request\",\"title\":\"Ship a PR\",\"query\":\"Help me implement a feature and open a PR. First, ask me to connect my code repo and project tracker so you can read the codebase and the related ticket directly. Then ask me the feature description, the framework/language, and the test approach, and write the code, add tests, and open the PR.\"},{\"id\":\"launch-a-business\",\"icon\":\"rocket\",\"title\":\"Launch a business\",\"query\":\"Help me launch a business. First, show me a diverse set of business archetypes as examples (services, SaaS, ecommerce, marketplace, content) and let me pick one or describe my own. Once I commit to an idea, ask me my goals and investment amount, then produce a go-to-market plan doc, a financial model spreadsheet, a pitch deck, and a deployed landing page.\"},{\"id\":\"run-deep-research\",\"icon\":\"list-search\",\"title\":\"Run deep research\",\"query\":\"Help me do extensive research. Ask me the topic and the decision I'm trying to make, then show 2–3 example framings of the research question with rationale and let me pick one or write my own. Once I commit, ask me the sources to include and how detailed the output should be, then produce a structured report.\"},{\"id\":\"monitor-a-website\",\"icon\":\"eye\",\"title\":\"Monitor a website\",\"query\":\"Help me monitor key websites for news, changes, and signals. Ask me what to watch, what counts as important, and the delivery format, then build a live website monitor dashboard and schedule alerts.\"},{\"id\":\"create-a-slide-deck\",\"icon\":\"presentation\",\"title\":\"Create a slide deck\",\"query\":\"Help me research a topic and turn it into a polished slide deck. Ask me the topic, the audience, the tone, the number of slides, and the key points to cover, then produce a downloadable PPTX with supporting charts and visualizations.\"},{\"id\":\"monitor-ai-releases\",\"icon\":\"sparkles\",\"title\":\"Monitor AI releases\",\"query\":\"Help me set up a daily AI-releases agent. First, show 5–6 example category bundles (frontier models, agents, infra, applied AI, open-source, research papers) and let me pick the bundles or write my own. Once I commit, ask me the sources and delivery format, then build a live dashboard and schedule the digest.\"}]}"
          },
